Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:01:00.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}从今往后的事 I will be there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:05.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}那天以后的事 With me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:10.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}夕阳西下之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.38,0:01:15.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}追逐着渐渐消失的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:21.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}谁都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.42,0:01:25.94,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}时光无法回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:30.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}呈现在眼前的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:34.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}毫无疑问的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:44.38,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}真正想见的人 在道路的另一头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:47.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}为了追逐那天的你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}迈出了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.96,0:01:57.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}这前面是无法成歌的Stories
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:01.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}I can’t tell what’s going on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:08.28,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}现在还不是寻找答案的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:13.32,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}现在已经无需用声音表达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:18.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}只要怀着心愿向前
